cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks and specifically on improving the scale-invariance of convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new model design, which could be considered as an artificial intelligence (cs.AI) contribution. The use of multi-column architecture and parameter sharing is also related to neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) processing.
